definitions.title: Hithpoïl.
definitions.body: Inf. [[לְהִתְנוֹסֵס]] Ps 60:6, acc. to some denom. from [[נֵס]] that it may be displayed, AV, cf. De; < v. [[נוס]]; Pt. [[מִתְנוֹסְסוֹת]] Zec 9:16 raised ? prominent ? ([[עַל־אַדְמָתוֹ]]; of precious stones, in fig.) very dub.; We Now del.; Gr [[מִתְנוֹחְחוֹת]]).
